snippet.title: Robothorium - Early Access trailer
snippet.description:
Steam page: http://store.steampowered.com/app/657090/Robothorium/

Robothorium is a futuristic turn-based, rogue-like RPG, where all your choices will have a direct impact on your revolution against Humankind. 
Gather your team of robots, choose your allies and lead your troops to the next Robots age.


Music: Robin Dussart and Dimitri Guindet
Voice: Nathalie Hitzel (https://m.facebook.com/natalie.hitzel?ref=bookmarks)
